OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMagistrates to get power to
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fjail offenders for a year  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Magistrates in England and Wales will  
OL,6, have greater sentencing powers to      
OL,7, enable them to take on more cases,     
OL,8, under plans to clear court backlogs.   
OL,10,FThe government plans to let magistrates
OL,11,Fsentence cases where the maximum       
OL,12,Fsentence is a year, rather than the    
OL,13,Fcurrent maximum of six months.         
OL,15,FIt would allow magistrates to hear     
OL,16,Fcases often held in Crown Court.       
OL,18,FBut criminal lawyers warn the plan may 
OL,19,Fbackfire, and defendants would still   
OL,20,Fhave the right to go before a jury.    
